description: Mardi Gras Express Gourmet Shaved Ice and Coffee is serving up the best shaved ice and gourmet coffee this side of New Orleans! The gourmet Snoballs include Crème Brulee, German Chocolate Cake, Bananas Foster, Peanut Butter Cup and Pineapple Upside -Down Cake. There are LOTS to choose from! For the café au lait, lattes, cappuccinos, and iced coffee, the trailer uses only Community Coffee, ordered straight from Baton Rouge. And they serve delicious pastries from local bakers right here in the Valley! Find it around the streets of Phoenix today!
name: Mardi Gras Express
